lass="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-bilibili"></i></a></div></div></div></div><div class="card-widget anzhiyu-right-widget" id="card-wechat" onclick="null"><div id="flip-wrapper"><div id="flip-content"><div class="face" style="background: url(https://img.neosey.com/neosey.png) center center / 100% no-repeat"></div><div class="back face" style="background: url(https://img.neosey.com/neosey-w.png) center center / 100% no-repeat"></div></div></div></div><div class="sticky_layout"><div class="card-widget" id="card-toc"><div class="item-headline"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-bars"></i><span>文章目录</span><span class="toc-percentage"></span></div><div class="toc-content"><ol class="toc"><li class="toc-item toc-level-1"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E7%86%AC%E5%A4%9C%E4%BC%9A%E6%9C%89%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E5%8D%B1%E5%AE%B3%EF%BC%9F"><span class="toc-number">1.</span> <span class="toc-text">经常熬夜会有哪些危害？</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-1"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%E7%86%AC%E5%A4%9C%E5%AF%B9%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%A4%E5%AE%B3%EF%BC%9F"><span class="toc-number">2.</span> <span class="toc-text">如何降低熬夜对身体的伤害？</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-1"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%8B%A5%E6%9C%89%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0"><span class="toc-number">3.</span> <span class="toc-text">如何拥有好的睡眠</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%E6%97%B6%E9%95%BF"><span class="toc-number">3.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">建议睡眠时长</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E5%85%A5%E7%9D%A1%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4"><span class="toc-number">3.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">建议入睡时间</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%85%8B%E6%9C%8D%E5%85%A5%E7%9D%A1%E5%9B%B0%E9%9A%BE%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%8F%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE"><span class="toc-nu